org.linqs.psl.parser

Class CommandLineLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.parser.CommandLineLoader

  • public class CommandLineLoader
extends Object
    Load the command line options into PSL Config's configuration values and log4j configuration appropriately. This is done by instatiating the object of type CommandLine and object log of type Logger.
